<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink400">
<l>maḷḷa raṉṉa maravan taḻīi</l>
<l>makaḷi raṉṉa vāṭukoṭi nuṭaṅku</l>
<l>marumpataṅ koṇṭa perumpata vēṉiṟ</l>
<l>kātal puṇarntaṉa ḷāki yāykaḻal</l>
<l>veñciṉa viralvēṟ kāḷaiyo</l>
<l>ṭiṉṟupuku tarumeṉa vantaṉṟu tūtē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The messenger has come,  </l>
<l>saying that she will enter [the village] today,  </l>
<l>together with young man in choice anklets, </l>
<l>[who has] hot anger and victorious spear, </l>
<l>after uniting [with him] out of love</l>
<l>in the great season of spring, </l>
<l>that has rare beauty of swaying creepers, resembing girls,</l>
<l>that lean and embrace Kaṭampa trees, resembling warriors. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
